- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as recommendation systems are often used in social networks and online platforms. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses how recommendation systems influence user interaction with the system. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss natural language processing techniques used in recommendation systems.
